                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='46341' id='24' type-v2='text' w='14036' x='0' y='53659'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>Insights</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1) BMW sales volumes remain broadly stable over time, with all regions following a similar trend and no major spikes or drops.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2) Sales are spread quite evenly across regions and models; a few models lead slightly, but no single model dominates.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3) Average pricing remains inelastic relative to engine size, with a slight peak at 3.5L.</run>
                    </formatted-text>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
